          <title>AWS Invests $10 Billion More in Ohio, Bringing 2030 Total to $23 Billion+</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Amazon Web Services (AWS) confirms plans to invest an additional $10 billion in Ohio by 2030, bringing the total investment to over $23 billion. The company aims to meet growing demand for cloud computing, artificial intelligence, and data centers.]]></description>
